data.description: Nestled in the heart of Fernley, this welcoming single-story awaits! Step inside and be greeted by a bright, open floor plan that hosts an abundance of natural light with sloped ceilings and luxurious laminate flooring. In the kitchen, enjoy a comfortable space with tile flooring and ample cabinetry alongside an ornamental backsplash, large sink and breakfast bar. A pristine primary suite features large glass doors, closet, and private bathroom with shower/tub combo. With carpet floors and neutral interiors, the additional bedrooms provide plenty of room for any lifestyle or purpose. Out back, unwind on your large patio and appreciate your fully-fenced yard, complete with simple shrubbery and low-maintenance xeriscaping. Other practical features include a two-car garage, laundry room with cabinetry, and ceiling fans throughout the home. This charming property is ready to welcome you home! Last photo came from Google Maps. This photo was used to show how beautiful the landscaping looks in the summertime. Buyer and Buyers agent to verify all information.
